reviewText: I Loved It! Its was a Great Show Hope to see him do this show live again soon in my area!

Seeing Elvis sing "God Give Me Strength" gave the chills and made me cry. If you like Elvis, or wish you could see him up close, this is a great piece. If you're not familiar with this tour, this is the one where fans come up on stage and spin a wheel to determine the song that Elvis will play next. Very cool.
